title: John Collison
deleted: John has a third sibling Tommy, who suffers from a rare form of Cerebral Palsy. John’s Mother Lily, published ‘Spastic Diplegia, Bilateral Cerebral Palsy’ which details to the re-occurring traits of the condition. Like his two brothers, Tommy also resides in San Francisco. Despite living in a city which is known for its thriving gay nightlife, and cannabis dispensaries, Tommy lives a very quiet life, often spending most of his time in his bedroom studying.
